The inof command enables iNOF and displays the iNOF view.
The undo inof command deletes all configurations in the inof view and disables the inof. The inof command enables iNOF and displays the iNOF view. The undo inof command deletes all configurations in the inof view and disables the inof. By default, iNOF is disabled. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE6885-SAN, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
